abstract: Cast of television show Mad Men and supporters gather at Museum of Modern Art for party to celebrate show's final episode.
lead_paragraph: Jon Hamm, Elisabeth Moss, Christina Hendricks, Matthew Weiner and others saluted the final season of the TV series that centered on the advertising industry.

headline.main: A Toast to the Final Episodes of ‘Mad Men’
headline.print_headline: The Last Office Party for ‘Mad Men’
